					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6227247#post-3847881</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-6227247/directive-a-42#post-3847881</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 23 Jun 2018 22:48:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I got excited when I saw &quot;Southern States&quot;, like, is this Dixieland Nightmare Magic in space?</p> <p>And, well, I guess not. :B My one qualm is the disconnect between the non-prose and prose portions of this piece. Like, I was really into the non-prose story telling, it was perfectly clear, and I kind of don't feel like I need a couple characters discussing what the documentation lays down.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
