								<wikidot:authorUserId>2303803</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The intro to my stuff for the timeline I'm building with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529782006" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" >9Volt</a></span> and a few others. You can start on 9volt's stuff <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/faster-than-light-prelude">here</a>. This whole setting that we're doing takes place after <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/amnesticization">Team Fuhgeddaboutit</a>'s doomsday, but this isn't a contest entry and it's not necessary to read that stuff unless you want a really in-depth look at what happened to the world.</p> <p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529782006" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" >9Volt</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varaxous" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2433554&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529782006" alt="Varaxous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2433554)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/varaxous" >Varaxous</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2320004&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529782006" alt="Rimple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2320004)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rimple" >Rimple</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2000367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1529782006" alt="WrongJohnSilver" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2000367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wrongjohnsilver" >WrongJohnSilver</a></span> for draft feedback. All images were made by me. The line drawing of a brain used in the schematic is here: <a href="https://pixabay.com/en/brain-diagram-anatomy-biology-40377/">https://pixabay.com/en/brain-diagram-anatomy-biology-40377/</a></p> 
